##########################################################
               THE SCALA TYPE DEBUGGER
##########################################################
Work in progress on Scala Type Debugger using Prefuse for
convenient UI.

Dependencies:
 - latest scala with instrumenting support
 - prefuse library

Both available in my repositories. You will also need xsbt for convenient compiling of type debugger.

How to start:
1) build scala with instrumenting support ('topic/contexterrors-events--instrumenting' branch),
   in all other steps we assume that $SCALA_INSTRUMENTING_HOME to its directory
2) create 'lib' directory
3) ln -s $SCALA_INSTRUMENTING_HOME/build/pack/lib/scala-library.jar lib/scala-library.jar (or symlink)
4) ln -s $SCALA_INSTRUMENTING_HOME/build/pack/lib/scala-compiler.jar lib/scala-compiler.jar (or symlink)
5) build prefuse and put prefuse-core-x.x.jar into lib
6) xsbt compile
7) export PATH=$SCALA_INSTRUMENTING_HOME/build/pack/bin:$PATH
8) scala -cp lib/prefuse-core-0.21.jar:target/scala-2.10.0-SNAPSHOT/classes scala.typedebugger.TypeDebuggerUI resources/code/src/A.scala

In future I will provide binaries for convience.
